snippet.title: Airlines gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Airlines, Dos PC game produced by Interactivision A/S in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/airline/1373/
It is an interesting game, a simulator. You must manage a firm passenger planes, everything related to economic and other staff.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
No sound recording available.
